OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780834280
OL,3,CChemicals strewn over busy motorway
OL,4,Cwhere van had crashed
OL,6,FTwo fire crews and specialist officers
OL,7,Fwere called to the A34 between
OL,8,FPeartree and Botley where a van had
OL,9,Fcrashed just before the Botley
OL,10,FInterchange, southbound on Friday
OL,11,Fafternoon (5 May).
OL,13,FTwo people in the van had managed to
OL,14,Fget out unharmed, but the vehicle had
OL,15,Fbeen carrying hazardous materials,
OL,16,Fwhich spilled across the carriageway.
OL,18,FThe chemical products had to be made
OL,19,Fsafe before the van could be moved.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
