PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780834280
OL,3,CChemicals strewn over busy motorway
OL,4,Cwhere van had crashed
OL,6,FFirefighters wore breathing equipment
OL,7,Fas they worked with recovery agents to
OL,8,Fclear the scene allowing the road to
OL,9,Fbe reopened almost three hours later.
OL,11,FTraffic was allowed to use one lane,
OL,12,Feasing delays, but a collision within
OL,13,Fthe tailback caused further disruption.
